          "reviewBody": "Best school ever . All the teacher's are good and there way of teaching is amazing. Principal is also good . But I gave 4 star because when we are in small classes 3,4&5 they provide notebook that are good but for since class 6 to 12 . They give us sheet to write. But when we attached the sheet in the file ,the sheet get tears and sheet came out from file . File's became too heavy and bags also became heavy . So the school have to see for that things .Please provide us notebook and the new session is starting so look at this thing for providing notebook",
          "publisher": {
