            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This branch of Somerville School is good. It has a big building. The location is good but reaching to this location is bit confusing if you are coming from Delhi or Noida. The school campus is good. It has an auditorium as well but the sitting arrangement is not good. This should have been gradually elevated one or the main stage in the auditorium should have been little elevated. Academia is good. Teachers are well trained and their students give the good results.",
